query:
SELECT 
  c.id,
  c.nome,
  c.projectId,
  c.pesquisaId,
  p.nome as project_name,
  ps.nome as pesquisa_name
FROM clientes c
LEFT JOIN projects p ON p.id = c.projectId
LEFT JOIN pesquisas ps ON ps.id = c.pesquisaId
WHERE c.nome LIKE '%Veolia%'
LIMIT 10;
